author: abhih1
body:
This PR adds the onnx models for EE+ and EE- , and 2022 average digi occupancy files for EB, EE- and EE+ for the inference in the autoencoder based online Ecal DQM feature to the dedicated data repository. 
To be used in PR: https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/41175
title: Add Ecal Endcaps onnx models and average occupancy files for ECAL MLDQM
